     usurperss:

     july ‘19 vs september ‘19
     image

     so here’s a tiny tutorial about light reflections (i’m no expert
     though!!)
     image image

     the drawing made in july is lacking on light reflections
     image image

     the one done in september looks much better since i paid attention
     to them

     Also remember that the intensity of the lighting depends on the
     material on which it is reflected, eg. glass / metal / fabrics etc.
     Glossy surfaces reflect the lighting more than matte surfaces

     another example:
     image image image

